				<td colspan="2"><div class="postbody">n Chakan. 
<br />

<br />
Rehabilitation for what? Its for punishment, you do a crime, do your time, and move on with life. Alot of guys that I've met from prison/the brig (the brig is way worse than ANY prison in the US) took it like men, and joke about it now. It may be a hiccup, but hey, your the one that @#%$ up, not everyone else. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
The Brig is the Marine/Navy Version of Prison, run by Marines who are pissed off because they have to work with people who @#%$ up every day. Which means you have 0 rights, and get to do -tons- of fun stuff...altho its not as bad as CCU (Corrective Custody Unit) which would be your idea of Prison Rehabilitation Chak <img src="images/smiles/smile.gif" alt="smile" border="0" /> You do rifle manual (Drill Movements) constantly, clean all day, PT (Physical Training) 3 times a day, run everywhere, speak when spoken to, etc... Mental/Physical Breakdown and Brainwashing. It works, i've seen some @#%$ up people go in there and come out pretty decent guys.<span class="gensmall"></span>


